11:47.152 --> 11:54.158
<i>♪ ♪</i>

12:02.902 --> 12:05.201
Oh, good. There you are.

12:05.204 --> 12:07.136
Rufus and I aren't having any luck.

12:07.139 --> 12:10.206
You?

12:10.209 --> 12:12.174
Keep looking.

12:12.177 --> 12:13.709
Are you okay?

12:13.712 --> 12:15.146
Yeah.

12:16.649 --> 12:18.049
Okay.

12:20.386 --> 12:27.392
<i>♪ ♪</i>

12:32.531 --> 12:34.730
- [door opens]
- Colonel Travis?

12:34.733 --> 12:36.699
Didn't mean to startle you, sir.

12:36.702 --> 12:38.100
Who the hell are you?

12:38.103 --> 12:39.602
Name's Flynn.

12:39.605 --> 12:42.271
And what're you doing in my office?

12:42.274 --> 12:43.873
I wanted to meet you.

12:43.876 --> 12:46.075
I'm an admirer of yours.

12:46.078 --> 12:49.512
You see, I'm here same reason as you.

12:49.515 --> 12:52.048
I'm a patriot,

12:52.051 --> 12:54.584
and I know it can't be easy.

12:54.587 --> 12:57.286
People call you a fanatic,

12:57.289 --> 12:59.522
but what you really are is a revolutionary

12:59.525 --> 13:01.724
fighting for freedom
against a corrupt power,

13:01.727 --> 13:03.559
and it's a lonely road.

13:03.562 --> 13:06.362
I understand that.

13:06.365 --> 13:09.065
I'm not that alone.

13:09.068 --> 13:10.533
I have men

13:10.536 --> 13:13.102
who told me to look out
for a tall son of a bitch

13:13.105 --> 13:16.906
with a funny accent.

13:16.909 --> 13:19.408
Apparently,

13:19.411 --> 13:22.278
he's dangerous.

13:22.281 --> 13:25.081
[gun clicks and fizzles]

13:25.084 --> 13:27.950
<i>♪ ♪</i>

13:27.953 --> 13:29.785
I'm sorry.

13:29.788 --> 13:32.221
<i>[suspenseful music]</i>

13:32.224 --> 13:33.956
Like I said,

13:33.959 --> 13:35.725
I'm an admirer of yours.

13:35.728 --> 13:37.727
<i>♪ ♪</i>

13:37.730 --> 13:40.062
You deserve a better fate.

13:40.065 --> 13:41.664
[gunshot]

13:41.667 --> 13:44.669
[men shouting]

13:46.305 --> 13:50.139
<i>♪ ♪</i>

13:50.142 --> 13:52.575
He's dead.

13:52.578 --> 13:54.844
This the man you warned
us about did this?

13:54.847 --> 13:56.681
Yeah, I think so.

13:58.851 --> 14:01.450
That gunshot came from a semi-automatic.

14:01.453 --> 14:03.686
Flynn was right here.

14:03.689 --> 14:06.088
<i>♪ ♪</i>

14:06.091 --> 14:07.590
I'll find him, sir.

14:07.593 --> 14:09.659
Not if we find him first.

14:09.662 --> 14:11.293
Come on.

14:11.296 --> 14:12.495
<i>♪ ♪</i>

14:12.498 --> 14:14.263
Ma'am.

14:14.266 --> 14:15.798
Excuse me.

14:15.801 --> 14:18.300
<i>♪</i>

14:18.303 --> 14:22.138
[indistinct chatter]

14:22.141 --> 14:23.973
What the hell happened?

14:23.976 --> 14:25.975
<i>♪ ♪</i>

14:25.978 --> 14:27.677
That's Colonel Travis.

14:27.680 --> 14:29.545
He was supposed to die
in battle in four days,

14:29.548 --> 14:31.147
but not now. Not like this.

14:31.150 --> 14:34.150
If he was gonna die anyway,
then why did Flynn do it?

14:34.153 --> 14:37.286
<i>♪ ♪</i>

14:37.289 --> 14:40.022
Oh, no, the letter.

14:40.025 --> 14:47.031
<i>♪ ♪</i>

14:56.842 --> 15:02.046
<i>♪ ♪</i>

15:06.456 --> 15:09.422
[men shouting in Spanish]

15:09.425 --> 15:12.425
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

15:12.428 --> 15:19.434
<i>♪ ♪</i>

15:21.237 --> 15:23.069
It's a red flag.

15:23.072 --> 15:24.504
What's a red flag mean?

15:24.507 --> 15:26.072
It means no quarter.

15:26.075 --> 15:27.607
No prisoners.

15:27.610 --> 15:29.442
Execute anyone who tries to surrender,

15:29.445 --> 15:31.050
which is not supposed to
happen, by the way.

15:31.074 --> 15:32.866
Santa Anna was supposed to let
the women and children go free.

15:32.890 --> 15:33.998
Am I missing something?

15:34.023 --> 15:35.584
None of this is supposed to happen.

15:35.609 --> 15:38.017
That army isn't supposed to be
here for another three days.

15:38.020 --> 15:39.752
Flynn must have found a way to change it.

15:39.755 --> 15:41.988
- But why?
- Must be about the letter.

15:41.991 --> 15:44.156
- What letter?
- Travis's famous

15:44.159 --> 15:45.758
"Victory or Death" letter.

15:45.761 --> 15:48.327
It's the one that was
re-printed in U.S. newspapers

15:48.330 --> 15:50.329
all over the country.
It's why we remember the Alamo.

15:50.332 --> 15:52.098
It's why they were able to
defeat Santa Anna

15:52.101 --> 15:53.599
in a few weeks.

15:53.602 --> 15:55.201
- It's only two sentences.
- Exactly.

15:55.204 --> 15:57.270
Because Travis was killed
before he was able to finish it.

15:57.273 --> 16:00.473
So, no letter, no Texas.

16:00.476 --> 16:01.607
<i>♪ ♪</i>

16:01.610 --> 16:02.942
Wyatt, are you even listening?

16:02.945 --> 16:04.377
All of this,

16:04.380 --> 16:07.615
and Flynn manages to
trap us in the Alamo.

16:08.951 --> 16:11.183
[chuckles wryly] Gotta hand it to him.

16:11.186 --> 16:12.818
Wyatt, I know that you want Flynn,

16:12.821 --> 16:14.353
but we really need you right now.

16:14.356 --> 16:16.222
[sighs]

16:16.225 --> 16:18.459
Wyatt, please.

16:20.663 --> 16:23.663
<i>[solemn music]</i>

16:23.666 --> 16:29.335
<i>♪ ♪</i>

16:29.338 --> 16:31.537
Rufus, you need to find a way out.

16:31.540 --> 16:32.846
A way out?

16:32.871 --> 16:34.507
There's two things everybody
knows about the Alamo.

16:34.510 --> 16:35.875
One, everybody dies.

16:35.878 --> 16:37.643
Two, they die because there's no way out.

16:37.646 --> 16:40.680
The Alamo didn't have
anyone as smart as you.

16:40.683 --> 16:43.583
Figure it out. Make a way if you have to.

16:43.586 --> 16:45.818
We need to get the women
and the children out.

16:45.821 --> 16:47.653
- Same with the letter.
- Well, like I said before,

16:47.656 --> 16:50.056
- Travis didn't finish it.
- Then finish it for him.

16:50.059 --> 16:52.425
<i>♪ ♪</i>

16:52.428 --> 16:54.226
I'm gonna try to buy us some time.

16:54.229 --> 16:57.730
Now, boys, the general sets
one foot outside that tent,

16:57.733 --> 17:00.066
and Davy here's gonna nail him.

17:00.069 --> 17:02.368
The man can part his hair 200 yards.

17:02.371 --> 17:05.171
- Ain't that right, Davy?
- I'll part his short hairs.

17:05.174 --> 17:07.373
- That he will.
- Colonel Bowie.

17:07.376 --> 17:09.709
- Yes, sir?
- A word?

17:09.712 --> 17:12.011
Excuse me, boys.

17:12.013 --> 17:14.246
What can I do for you?

17:14.249 --> 17:15.580
I can help you.

17:15.584 --> 17:17.249
I just need command of some of your men.

17:17.252 --> 17:18.584
What was your name again?

17:18.587 --> 17:21.287
Master Sergeant Wyatt Logan.

17:21.290 --> 17:22.887
U.S. Army.

17:22.891 --> 17:24.089
My friend's working on a plan

17:24.093 --> 17:25.358
to get the women and the children out,

17:25.361 --> 17:26.791
but we need to buy him some time.

17:26.795 --> 17:28.260
Everyone's safe for now. Thanks.

17:28.262 --> 17:31.197
Not for long, sir.

17:31.200 --> 17:34.767
Look, don't go putting us in
the ground just yet, all right?

17:34.770 --> 17:37.603
Colonel Fannin and his troops
are on their way as we speak.

17:37.606 --> 17:39.939
No. They aren't.

17:39.942 --> 17:42.141
No reason to lose faith, son.

17:42.144 --> 17:45.711
No one is getting out of here alive.

17:45.714 --> 17:48.114
Do you understand me?

17:48.117 --> 17:50.549
Santa Anna is waiting on reinforcements,

17:50.552 --> 17:52.251
and when they come, which they will,

17:52.254 --> 17:53.619
tomorrow,

17:53.622 --> 17:55.554
he's gonna come over this wall

17:55.557 --> 17:57.089
and in 20 minutes
you're all gonna be dead.

17:57.092 --> 17:58.491
- Wyatt.
- So we need to get

17:58.494 --> 17:59.825
the women and the children out.

17:59.828 --> 18:01.460
You listen to me.

18:01.463 --> 18:03.429
I don't care how scared you are,

18:03.432 --> 18:05.665
you will not speak that
way around my men.

18:05.668 --> 18:07.767
You got that?

18:07.770 --> 18:14.273
<i>♪ ♪</i>

18:14.276 --> 18:15.562
_

18:15.587 --> 18:17.504
_

18:17.532 --> 18:19.525
_

18:19.677 --> 18:21.645
_

18:25.413 --> 18:28.039
_

18:28.501 --> 18:31.117
_

18:31.142 --> 18:35.609
_

18:35.940 --> 18:37.649
_

18:38.256 --> 18:41.043
_

18:41.043 --> 18:44.278
_

18:44.278 --> 18:49.158
_

18:49.659 --> 18:51.921
_

18:52.424 --> 18:54.792
_

18:54.817 --> 18:57.216
<i>No, no, no, no, no, no es. No es.</i>

18:57.219 --> 18:58.994
_

18:59.582 --> 19:01.378
_

19:01.851 --> 19:03.439
_

19:05.035 --> 19:07.004
